702124f-a.text:
2511 Westchester Avenue(right), at the N.E. corner of St. Peters Avenue,showing the parish house of St. Peters Protestant Episcopal Church and the old carriage sheds. In the left background is Public School No. 12, on Frisby
Avenue.
Brown Brothers
NO REPRODUCTIONS  June,1926

702123f-b.text:
2511 Westchester Avenue, at the N. E. corner of St.
Peters Avenue, showing the Parish House of St. Peters
Protestant Episcopal Church, seen from the latter Avenue.
View 3 shows the old carriage sheds in rear of the house,
on St. Peters Avenue. Shown, too, is the rear of an apart-
ment house fronting on Frisby Avenue.

July 9, 1928
Views 1,2,3
